store uv_pattern at (2, 3, 2) colour UV;
store uv_pattern at (3, 2, 2) colour UV;
store uv_pattern at (3, 3, 2) colour UV;
store uv_pattern at (4, 2, 2) colour UV;
store uv_pattern at (4, 3, 2) colour UV;

